name: Woven Leather Bracelet - Cherrywood
description:
This bracelet is made from high quality leather woven into a bolo cord.

It is a great design for men or women and looks really natural and earthy.

The leather measures approximately 5mm in diameter, and it is finished with a silver plated magnetic closure.

If you need a custom size, please just let me know, it's no problem!

Since these bracelets are made to order, plese allow an additional 1-2 days for delivery. 

Thank you so much for looking, and as always, feel free to convo me about different quantities and colors.

Have a great day!!!! 

If you would like to check out more of my designs, please see my etsy shop: www.adriadiane.etsy.com

name: Triple African Turquoise and Leather Wrap Bracelet
description:
This bracelet features 4mm African Turquoise stone beads woven onto black Greek leather. 

All beads are double strung to ensure durability.

This bracelet is intended to wrap around the wrist three times, and may be worn alone, or with others for a fun layered look.

It has a hand stamped silver button closure, and measures 19.5 " beaded, but is adjustable up to 20.75".

Thank you!
